room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by Escape Goat in Orlando
room_address: 1165 E Plant St, Winter Garden, FL 34787
room_description: Welcome, recruits, to your first day of training! You arrive at the Area 51 facility to meet with your trainer, Professor Vangeli and to start your new assignment in the catalog department. It doesn't take long to realize why many recruits don't last very long in this department... Do you have what it takes to survive your first day of training?
